Unity script to access foottroller data through local network.
Use FoottrollerNet.cs to get Foottroller control and data from a Foottroller hub.
FoottrollerCtrl.cs is an example of using the control and data from FoottrolerNet.cs for movement control.
A sample VR game for Unity is provided, which uses the two scripts to achieve natural VR movement control with Foottroller.
https://github.com/smoothmover/foottrollersupport/releases/tag/UnitySampleGame

